---
title: "_getAssetPrice (PriceManager)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_load: load priceInfo and feedInfo for asset
    q_load --> q_set_streams: price = priceInfo.usdPrice, updatedAt = priceInfo.timestamp
    q_set_streams --> q_check_stale: minTimestamp = block.timestamp - stalenessThreshold
    q_check_stale --> q_check_datafeed: updatedAt < minTimestamp
    q_check_stale --> q_validate: updatedAt >= minTimestamp
    q_check_datafeed --> q_validate: usdDataFeed == address(0)
    q_check_datafeed --> q_fetch_feed: usdDataFeed != address(0)
    q_fetch_feed --> q_compare_ts: (answer, dataFeedUpdatedAt) = usdDataFeed.latestRoundData()
    q_compare_ts --> q_validate: updatedAt >= dataFeedUpdatedAt
    q_compare_ts --> q_use_feed: updatedAt < dataFeedUpdatedAt
    q_use_feed --> q_scale_feed: price = answer, updatedAt = dataFeedUpdatedAt
    q_scale_feed --> q_validate: scale price to 18 decimals
    q_validate --> q_compute_valid: isValid = !isZero AND !isStale
    q_compute_valid --> q_check_validation: withValidation?
    q_check_validation --> [*]: !withValidation, return (price, updatedAt, isValid)
    q_check_validation --> q_val_zero: withValidation
    q_val_zero --> q_error_zero: price == 0
    q_error_zero --> [*]: revert ZeroFeedData
    q_val_zero --> q_val_stale: price > 0
    q_val_stale --> q_error_stale: isStale
    q_error_stale --> [*]: revert StaleFeedData
    q_val_stale --> [*]: return (price, updatedAt, true)

    note right of q_check_stale
        INV-001: Data Streams price is prioritized over data feed
        INV-002: Fallback to data feed only when streams price is stale AND feed is configured
        INV-003: Most recent timestamp wins between streams and data feed
    end note
